{"tid":1772431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[128 維園見] 百萬人攻略","createTime":"2019-12-06T15:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:23:44.000Z","uid":268158,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0543484aa057352ee4bb700a14e2cb1be42b458","tid":1772431,"uid":268158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"想再出現百萬人級的遊行，咁就要老人小孩和理非都出現<br />\n亦即係話遊行一定要和平進行<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得運動的成功模式？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非暖場 &gt; 勇武升級</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以今次請勇武化身和理非，先做一次暖場遊行<br />\n當百萬人和平遊行完，暴已止，亂已制，訴求表達完，政府都唔做野<br />\n咁我地就有大條道理去將行動全面升級<br />\n<br />\n今次勇武唔好出黎保護和理非喇<br />\n勇武為大家食彈食得太多喇<br />\n如果班狗今次都係亂射彈，咁就由得和理非自己頂一次啦<br />\n如果勇武出場，班狗又會話因為有人搞事先射彈<br />\n所以請唔好送個藉口俾佢地<br />\n<br />\n我地做多次6月9日的和平遊行好嗎？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">不堵路、不挖磚、不擲物、不撚狗<br />\n邊個搞事邊個就係鬼</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊成，先黎一次和平百萬行，再不回應就全面開戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔需要暖場，唔需要門面功夫，直接開佢波"},{"pid":"f6d3ec17844d4b042757e14060dd34becb458b2c","tid":1772431,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeyLg53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeyLg53.gif&h=4db44cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeyLg53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeyLg53.gif&h=4db44cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeyLg53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeyLg53.gif&h=4db44cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeyLg53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeyLg53.gif&h=4db44cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeyLg53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2